United Left Coalition (<span style="color: [+ spd_colour +];">**SPD**</span> + <span style="color: [+ uspd_colour +];">**USPD**</span> + <span style="color: [+ kpd_colour +];">**KPD**</span>[? if sapd_formed:&nbsp;+ <span style="color: #9B0000;">**SAPD**</span>?]): [+ left_coalition_bremen +]% 

Weimar Coalition (<span style="color: [+ spd_colour +];">**SPD**</span> + [? if not lvp_formed: <span style="color: [+ ddp_colour +];">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span>?][? if lvp_formed: <span style="color: #FFCC00;">**LVP**</span>?]<span style="color: #000000;"> + **Z**</span>): [+ weimar_coalition_bremen +]% 

Grand Coalition (<span style="color: [+ spd_colour +];">**SPD**</span> + [? if not lvp_formed: <span style="color: [+ ddp_colour +];">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: [+ dvp_colour +];">**DVP**</span>?][? if lvp_formed: <span style="color: #FFCC00;">**LVP**</span>?]<span style="color: #000000;"> + **Z**</span> + <span style="color: #AFAFAF;">**Others**</span>): [+ grand_coalition_bremen +]%

Bourgeois Coalition (<span style="color: #000000;">**Z**</span> + [? if not lvp_formed: <span style="color: [+ ddp_colour +];">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: [+ dvp_colour +];">**DVP**</span>?][? if lvp_formed: <span style="color: #FFCC00;">**LVP**</span>?] [? if kvp_formed :+ <span style="color: #0087DC;">**KVP**</span> ?]+ <span style="color: #0087DC;">**VRP**</span> + <span style="color: #b8996f;">**WP**</span> + <span style="color: #AFAFAF;">**Others**</span> + [? if kvp_formed:&nbsp;+ <span style="color: #0087DC;">**KVP**</span> ?]): [+ true_bourgeois_coalition_bremen +]%

Right-Wing Coalition (<span style="color: [+ dnvp_colour +];">**DNVP**</span> + <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**NSDAP**</span> + <span style="color: [+ dvp_colour +];">**DVP**</span> + <span style="color: #b8996f;">**WP**</span>): [+ right_coalition_bremen +]%

@bremen_coalition_menu


- @weimar_coalition_bremen
- @grand_coalition_bremen
- @bourgeois_coalition_bremen
- @left_coalition_bremen
- @spd_majority_bremen
- @right_wing_coalition_bremen
- @no_coalition_bremen
- @bremen_coalition_creator_option

@weimar_coalition_bremen
title: A Weimar Coalition will be formed
choose-if: weimar_coalition_bremen > 50 and z_relation >= 25
on-arrival: bremen_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; z_relation += 2; ddp_relation += 3; bremen_gov = "Weimar"

@grand_coalition_bremen
title: A Grand Coalition will be formed
choose-if: grand_coalition_bremen > 50 and z_relation >= 25 and dvp_relation >= 35
on-arrival: bremen_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; z_relation += 2; dvp_relation += 3; bremen_gov = "Grand"

@bourgeois_coalition_bremen
title: A bourgeois coalition must be formed
choose-if: true_bourgeois_coalition_bremen > 50
view-if: weimar_coalition_bremen < 50 and right_coalition_bremen < 50
on-arrival: bremen_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; bremen_gov = "Bourgeois"

@left_coalition_bremen
title: A Coalition of the Left will be formed
subtitle: We will work alongside the KPD
choose-if: left_coalition_bremen > 50 and kpd_relation >= 40
on-arrival: bremen_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; unemployed_kpd += 3; new_middle_others -= 2; new_middle_dvp -= 1; new_middle_spd += 1; bremen_gov = "Left"

@spd_majority_bremen
title: SPD majority
subtitle: We don't need any coalition partners
view-if: spd_r_bremen > 50
on-arrival: bremen_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; workers_spd += 1; workers_dnvp -= 2; new_middle_spd += 1; new_middle_others -= 1; bremen_gov = "SPD"

@right_wing_coalition_bremen
title: The DNVP and DVP will work alongside the NSDAP
subtitle: This should not have happened
choose-if: right_coalition_bremen > 50
view-if: right_coalition_bremen > 50
on-arrival: bremen_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; rural_nsdap += 2; dvp_relation -= 2; bremen_gov = "Right"

This can't end well...

@no_coalition_bremen
title: There is no possible government arrangement
subtitle: New elections will be called...
on-arrival: bremen_election_2_trigger_time = time + 3; new_middle_dnvp += 1
view-if: weimar_coalition_bremen < 50 and right_coalition_bremen < 50

@bremen_coalition_creator_option
title: Custom Coalition Creator (Test)
subtitle: Dear Test Players, if you see this, please tell me what you think
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = spd_r_bremen; bremen_spd = "government"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

@bremen_coalition_creator
title: Coalition Creator

Current support: [+ bremen_coalition_r +]%

- @bremen_invite_kpd: Invite the <span style="color: [+ kpd_colour +];">**KPD**</span>
- @bremen_invite_sapd: Invite the <span style="color: [+ sapd_colour +];">**SAPD**</span>
- @bremen_invite_uspd: Invite the <span style="color: [+ uspd_colour +];">**USPD**</span>
- @bremen_invite_ddp: Invite the <span style="color: [+ ddp_colour +];">**DDP**</span>
- @bremen_invite_lvp: Invite the <span style="color: [+ lvp_colour +];">**LVP**</span>
- @bremen_invite_z: Invite the <span style="color: [+ z_colour +];">Center Party</span>
- @bremen_invite_wp: Invite the <span style="color: #CEDD8A;">Home Owners</span>
- @bremen_invite_others: Invite the <span style="color: [+ other_colour +];">**Others**</span>
- @bremen_invite_dvp: Invite the <span style="color: [+ dvp_colour +];">**DVP**</span>
- @bremen_invite_wp: Invite the <span style="color: #b8996f;">**WP**</span>
- @bremen_invite_dnvp: Invite the <span style="color: [+ dnvp_colour +];">**BCVP**</span>
- @bremen_check_out: Check out.
- @bremen_drop_kpd: Drop the <span style="color: [+ kpd_colour +];">**KPD**</span>
- @bremen_drop_sapd: Drop the <span style="color: [+ sapd_colour +];">**SAPD**</span>
- @bremen_drop_uspd: Drop the <span style="color: [+ uspd_colour +];">**USPD**</span>
- @bremen_drop_ddp: Drop the <span style="color: [+ ddp_colour +];">**DDP**</span>
- @bremen_drop_lvp: Drop the <span style="color: [+ lvp_colour +];">**LVP**</span>
- @bremen_drop_z: Drop the <span style="color: [+ z_colour +];">Center Party</span>
- @bremen_drop_wp: Drop the <span style="color: #CEDD8A;">Home Owners</span>
- @bremen_drop_others: Drop the <span style="color: [+ other_colour +];">**Others**</span>
- @bremen_drop_dvp: Drop the <span style="color: [+ dvp_colour +];">**DVP**</span>
- @bremen_drop_wp: Drop the <span style="color: #b8996f;">**WP**</span>
- @return_to_bremen: Return


@bremen_invite_kpd
view-if: kpd_r_bremen > 0 and not bremen_kpd = "government"
choose-if: kpd_relation >= 55 and bremen_dvp == "opposition" and bremen_wp == "opposition" and (not bremen_z == "government" or z_leader == "Joos" or z_leader == "Kaiser")
subtitle: The <span style="color: [+ kpd_colour +];">**KPD**</span> will demand radical policies.
unavailable-subtitle: [? if  kpd_relation < 55: We need better relations. ?][? if not bremen_dvp == "opposition": They are not really pleased about our partners. ?]
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = bremen_coalition_r + kpd_r_bremen; bremen_kpd = "government"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

@bremen_invite_sapd
view-if: sapd_r_bremen > 0 and not bremen_sapd = "government"
choose-if: sapd_relation >= 50 and bremen_dvp == "opposition" and bremen_wp == "opposition" and (not bremen_z == "government" or z_leader == "Joos" or z_leader == "Kaiser")
subtitle: The <span style="color: [+ sapd_colour +];">**SAPD**</span> will demand radical policies.
unavailable-subtitle: [? if  sapd_relation < 50: We need better relations. ?][? if not bremen_dvp == "opposition": They are not really pleased about our partners. ?]
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = bremen_coalition_r + sapd_r_bremen; bremen_sapd = "government"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

@bremen_invite_uspd
view-if: uspd_r_bremen > 0 and not bremen_uspd = "government"
choose-if: uspd_relation >= 40 and bremen_wp == "opposition" and (not bremen_z == "government" or z_leader == "Joos" or z_leader == "Kaiser" or uspd_ideology == "Orthodox Marxism")
subtitle: [? if not uspd_ideology == "Orthodox Marxism": The <span style="color: [+ uspd_colour +];">**USPD**</span> will demand radical policies. ?][? if uspd_ideology == "Orthodox Marxism": Center Marxists are flexible. ?]
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = bremen_coalition_r + uspd_r_bremen; bremen_uspd = "government"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

@bremen_invite_ddp
view-if: ddp_r_bremen > 0 and not bremen_ddp = "government"
choose-if: ddp_relation >= 20 and (not bremen_kpd == "government" or kpd_leader == "Conciliators")
subtitle: [? if ddp_relation >= 65: The <span style="color: [+ ddp_colour +];">**DDP**</span> loves you! ?]
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = bremen_coalition_r + ddp_r_bremen; bremen_ddp = "government"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

@bremen_invite_lvp
view-if: lvp_r_bremen > 0 and not bremen_lvp = "government"
choose-if: lvp_relation >= 45 and (not bremen_kpd == "government" or kpd_leader == "Conciliators")
subtitle: [? if lvp_relation >= 75: The <span style="color: [+ lvp_colour +];">**LVP**</span> loves you! ?]
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = bremen_coalition_r + lvp_r_bremen; bremen_lvp = "government"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

@bremen_invite_z
view-if: z_r_bremen > 0 and not bremen_z = "government"
choose-if: z_relation >= 25 and (not bremen_kpd == "government" or kpd_leader == "Conciliators")
subtitle: [? if z_r_bremen >= spd_r_bremen: The <span style="color: [+ z_colour +];">Center Party</span> demands the minister-president. ?] They would love to sign a concordat
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = bremen_coalition_r + z_r_bremen; bremen_z = "government"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

@bremen_invite_dvp
view-if: dvp_r_bremen > 0 and not bremen_dvp = "government"
choose-if: dvp_relation >= 35 and bremen_kpd == "opposition" and bremen_sapd == "opposition"
subtitle: The <span style="color: [+ dvp_colour +];">**DVP**</span> demands tax cuts.
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = bremen_coalition_r + dvp_r_bremen; bremen_dvp = "government"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

@bremen_invite_hb
view-if: hb_r_bremen > 0 and not bremen_dvp = "government"
choose-if: ddp_relation >= 60 and bremen_kpd == "opposition" and bremen_sapd == "opposition"
subtitle: The <span style="color: #CEDD8A;">Home Owners</span> demands owner friendly policies.
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = bremen_coalition_r + hb_r_bremen; bremen_hb = "government"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

@bremen_invite_others
view-if: true_other_r_bremen > 0 and not bremen_true_others = "government"
choose-if: ddp_relation >= 70 and z_relation >= 35
subtitle: The <span style="color: [+ other_colour +];">**Others**</span> are a little conservative.
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = bremen_coalition_r + true_other_r_bremen; bremen_true_others = "government"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

@bremen_invite_wp
view-if: wp_r_bremen > 0 and not bremen_wp = "government"
choose-if: dvp_relation >= 70 and bremen_kpd == "opposition" and bremen_sapd == "opposition" and bremen_uspd == "opposition"
subtitle: The <span style="color: #b8996f;">**WP**</span> is a little conservative and will demand tax cuts.
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = bremen_coalition_r + wp_r_bremen; bremen_wp = "government"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

Why did you do this?

@bremen_invite_dnvp
view-if: dnvp_r_bremen > 0
choose-if: dnvp_relation >= 900
subtitle: This won't happen.
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

Why are you so desperate?

@bremen_check_out
choose-if: bremen_coalition_r >= 50
subtitle: We can form a coalition!
unavailable-subtitle: We need more partners
on-arrival: bremen_gov = "Social-Catholic" if bremen_spd == "government" and bremen_z == "government"; bremen_gov = "Weimar" if bremen_spd == "government" and bremen_z == "government" and bremen_ddp == "government"; bremen_gov = "Grand" if bremen_spd == "government" and bremen_z == "government" and bremen_dvp == "government"; bremen_gov = "Left" if bremen_spd == "government" and bremen_kpd == "government"; bremen_gov = "Popular-Front" if bremen_spd == "government" and bremen_z == "government" and bremen_kpd == "government"; bremen_gov = "Social-Democratic" if bremen_uspd == "government" and not bremen_kpd == "government" and not bremen_z == "government"; bremen_gov = "Social-Liberal" if bremen_ddp == "government" and not bremen_z == "government" and bremen_spd == "government"  

Congrats you have formed a [+ bremen_gov +] Coalition with [+ bremen_coalition_r +]% parliamentary support!

@bremen_drop_kpd
view-if: bremen_kpd = "government"
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = bremen_coalition_r - kpd_r_bremen; bremen_kpd = "opposition"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

@bremen_drop_sapd
view-if: bremen_sapd = "government"
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = bremen_coalition_r - sapd_r_bremen; bremen_sapd = "opposition"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

@bremen_drop_uspd
view-if: bremen_uspd = "government"
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = bremen_coalition_r - uspd_r_bremen; bremen_uspd = "opposition"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

@bremen_drop_ddp
view-if: bremen_ddp = "government"
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = bremen_coalition_r - ddp_r_bremen; bremen_ddp = "opposition"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

@bremen_drop_lvp
view-if: bremen_lvp = "government"
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = bremen_coalition_r - lvp_r_bremen; bremen_lvp = "opposition"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

@bremen_drop_z
view-if: bremen_z = "government"
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = bremen_coalition_r - z_r_bremen; bremen_z = "opposition"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

@bremen_drop_dvp
view-if: bremen_dvp = "government"
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = bremen_coalition_r - dvp_r_bremen; bremen_dvp = "opposition"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

@bremen_drop_hb
view-if: bremen_hb = "government"
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = bremen_coalition_r - hb_r_bremen; bremen_hb = "opposition"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

@bremen_drop_others
view-if: bremen_true_others = "government"
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = bremen_coalition_r - true_other_r_bremen; bremen_true_others = "opposition"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

@bremen_drop_wp
view-if: bremen_wp = "government"
on-arrival: bremen_coalition_r = bremen_coalition_r - wp_r_bremen; bremen_wp = "opposition"
go-to: bremen_coalition_creator

It is better that way.


@return_to_bremen
on-arrival: bremen_spd = "opposition"
go-to: bremen_coalition_menu
